&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role: What&#39;s in the Box&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3,0&quot;&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;36&quot;&gt;Site QA/QC Specialist&lt;/strong&gt; to join our dynamic, fast-growing team in &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;100&quot;&gt;Bleiswijk&lt;/strong&gt;. As a key member of the Food Safety &amp;amp; Quality Assurance (FSQA) department, you will drive the initiatives that define the quality of every HelloFresh box.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3,1&quot;&gt;You will be on the front lines of our fulfillment center, optimizing daily processes and partnering closely with operational teams to ensure a gold standard of quality for our customers. When challenges arise or unannounced audits occur, you are the expert who steps forward to ensure compliance and maintain our high operational momentum.&lt;/p&gt;
