&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Design, implement, and refine internal quality processes to bridge the gap between high-speed operations and flawless food safety.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Partnership: &lt;/strong&gt;Work side-by-side with production and logistics teams to embed a &quot;quality-first&quot; mindset and optimize daily fulfillment workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Audit Leadership: &lt;/strong&gt;Take a leading role in conducting internal audits and GMP rounds, while serving as the key point of contact for supervising external and unannounced audits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Improvement Projects:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with the wider Site Quality team to spearhead strategic projects that drive the evolution of the HelloFresh box.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quality Feedback Loop:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage the investigation and follow-up for supplier non-conformities and consumer complaints, turning feedback into actionable site improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll bring: The Ingredients&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;2-5 years work experience in a quality function within the food industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;You are accurate and goal oriented.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;You are able to present in a fast-paced and continuously changing work environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;You enjoy working with other teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;You have experience with quality systems such as IFS, BRC or FSSC22000.&lt;/li&gt;
