&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll lead a team of roughly 100 FTE across three departments, setting the pace and the standard for how we move product safely, efficiently, and at scale. This is a high-visibility role with real decision-making authority. You&#39;ll have a direct line to the Site Lead and a seat at the table when it matters most.&lt;/p&gt;
